		<h2><a id="titleHref" href="/story/2013/02/27/1190210/-Poll-GOP-losing-spending-debate">Poll: GOP losing spending debate</a><span style="white-space: nowrap"></span></h2>
		
		<p class="author"><span>by</span> <a href="/user/Jed Lewison">Jed Lewison</a><a class="ajax type-user do-hotlist do-updateContent size-tiny off altTooltip" alt="Follow this author" href="#?friend_id=191280&is_stream=1">Follow</a> <span class="for">for</span> <a href="/blog/main">Daily Kos</a></p>
    
    <ul class="front-page-share clearfix">
      
      <li style="margin-left: 0px"><div class="fb-like" data-send="false" data-layout="button_count" data-width="450" data-show-faces="false" data-href="http://www.dailykos.com/story/2013/02/27/1190210/-Poll-GOP-losing-spending-debate"></div></li>
      <li><a href="https://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-count="horizontal" data-via="dailykos" data-related="markos" data-url="http://www.dailykos.com/story/2013/02/27/1190210/-Poll-GOP-losing-spending-debate" data-text="Poll: GOP losing spending debate">Tweet</a></li>
          
		  <li style="margin-left: 0px"><a href="#" class="email">Email</a></li>
		  
		  <li><a href="/story/2013/02/27/1190210/-Poll-GOP-losing-spending-debate#comments" class="comments comment_count_with_new" data-story_id="1190210" data-comment_count="51">51 Comments</a></li>
