<p>the meme.</p>
<p>The Republicans don't care about spending, or the deficit. &nbsp;They only care about decimating the safety net, and campaign that they started back during the FDR days and have continued since. &nbsp;We need to change the meme to this, so that it's not longer about spending per se, but about what kind of spending is really necessary to "promote the general welfare."</p>

